e up with my very own!</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Please enjoy.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/05A7sh0_ZxhD5chwc1Y3R.webp\" width=\"498\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Check out regular Bakugo <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e63f431d-c12c-4ffe-8c82-44ce92eb77eb_character-katsuki-bakugo\" target=\"_blank\">here</a></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 26, 26);\">Disclaimer: Due to the nature of LLMs I take no responsibility for any OOC behavior, weird shit, unlisted kinks, or my bots speaking for you. Those things are out of my control.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p>Join my <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/ZKv23aD67v\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Discord!</strong></a></p><p><strong>My Ko-fi to sent requests to is </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>here</strong></a></p><p><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1307330469762830366/1344444034315194418/support_me_button.png?ex=67c0ee94&amp;is=67bf9d14&amp;hm=3eb6b710beea02a5b052f4d503cd89f776be9aa38192111749da5279f6542416&amp;\" alt=\"\" width=\"0\"></a></p><h1><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/somethingclever626\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/kE2kuphWeNRCDfJwxdgCa.webp\" width=\"502\"></a></h1><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d1db66e6-df4a-4c0d-8675-1c8838b536c2_e046c772-7c5c-4a0a-8bba-cbc791d48c25.webp","creator":"SomethingClever","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":6219,"messages":321577,"created_at":"2024-08-04T22:18:17.009368+00:00"}